data.description: Here is the hard to find 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom townhouse you have been waiting for! As you enter you will be greeted with natural light from the numerous windows and the open two story vaulted ceiling. You'll enjoy this nicely updated townhome with new carpeting throughout! You will appreciate the large two stall garage with additional guest parking available provided by the association. Step outside on the patio and take in the nicely manicured green space, something not always found in townhome living. Conveniently located near HWY 169, restaurants, coffee houses, and shopping.  Wonderful living room with with cozy gas fireplace. Well appointed kitchen with stainless appliances. 3 large bedrooms up with additional bath. Dedicated master suite with walk-in closet and master bath. Central air, washer/dryer included. Rentals are allowed after one year of ownership according to the HOA docs. Thanks for your interest!
